data.description: This delightful single story home perched on a corner lot is move in ready. Nice open floor plan. Recent upgrades/improvements include; front door, garage door, all windows, rain gutters and water heater. Walking distance to Comanche Lookout Park. Convenient to Loop 1604, IH35, JBSA Randolph, Forum Shopping/Dining. Terrific NEISD Schools.
